        <mxCell id="t_shared_items" value="• All go through the same /api/ai/fill endpoint&lt;br&gt;• All use SSE streaming with fetchSseStream + parsePartialJson&lt;br&gt;• First chunk triggers pushUndo (for Ctrl+Z)&lt;br&gt;• Stream ends → doSave (800ms debounce) → SQLite via Server Action&lt;br&gt;• FixedFields animation (5s highlight on changed fields)&lt;br&gt;• Error → setAiError; Abort → setAiError('Request cancelled')" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=14;" vertex="1" parent="1">
